text: Jacob Elordi (born June 26, 1997) is an Australian actor. He played the role of Noah Flynn in The Kissing Booth movie series. In 2019, Elordi began playing Nate Jacobs in the HBO television series Euphoria. ==Filmography== * Carpe Liam (2015) ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Australian movie actors Category:Australian television actors Category:Australian voice actors Category:Actors from Brisbane
